Package cat.nyaa.nyaacore.component

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IComponent  
    IDamageStatistic
    Damage statistic is introduced by NyaaUtils which tracks how much damage does every player make.
    ISystemBalance
    The idea of "system balance" is introduced in HamsterEconomyHelper, which says, all fees charged by the system shall be returned to players.
    ITemporaryStorage
    Temporary storage is used to deliver items to players reliably.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NyaaComponent
    Component APIs are designed to facilitate interoperability between NyaaCat plugins.
